{"serial": "44004", "department_serial": 41, "code": "EC2054", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "The Central Bank and Financial Institutions", "ch": "中央銀行與金融機構"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chih-Hsing Liao"], "ch": ["廖志興"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "308"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "經濟學系", "en": "Department of Economics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 69, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "中央銀行與金融機構是一學期的入門課程, 這個課程介紹關於中央銀行與金融市場的一些基本觀念與重要議題. 除此之外, 這門課也提供一些分析工具, 並且用來它解釋與分析各種的總體經濟現象.", "en": "This is a one-semester introductory course to the Central Bank and financial institution. This course introduces some important issues and fundamental concepts in the Central Bank and the financial market. Furthermore, this course will also provide some analytical tools and then apply them to various macroeconomic phenomena."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 課程介紹\n2. 金融結構的經濟分析\n3. 已開發國家的金融危機\n4. 新興市場的金融危機\n5. 銀行理監的經濟分析\n6. 從全球的觀點看中央銀行\n7. 貨幣供給過程, 複習\n8. 期中考\n9. 貨幣政策工具\n10. 貨幣政策的目標與執行\n11. 貨幣需求理論\n12. IS-LM 模型\n13. 總合需求與供給分析\n14. 貨幣政策理論\n15. 複習\n16. 期末考\n“課程可能因教學需要而有所微調“", "en": "1. Introduction\n2. An Economic Analysis of Financial Structure\n3. Financial Crises in Advanced Economies\n4. Financial Crises in Emerging Market Economies\n5. Economic Analysis of Financial Regulation\n6. Central Banks: A Global Perspective\n7. The Money Supply Process, Review\n8. Midterm Exam\n9. Tools of Monetary Policy\n10. The Conduct of Monetary policy: Strategy and Tactics\n11. Quantity Theory, Inflation, and the Demand for Money\n12. IS-LM Model\n13. Aggregate Demand and Supply Analysis\n14. Monetary Policy Theory\n15. Review\n16. Final Exam"}, "textbook": {"ch": "貨幣銀行學 13版 (2019) 李榮謙 編著.\nFrederi